data.title: Our members
data.meta_description: The Local Government Information Unit's members include councils, trade unions, charities, public sector partners and private sector organisations.
data.text:
The LGIU provides corporate membership for organisations in England and Wales, Scotland, Ireland and Australia. If you are an elected representative or staff member at one of the organisations below, you are an LGIU member.

If you are an LGIU member, sign up on the website to access your member-only resources.
